381
00:17:11.040 --> 00:17:12.875
Be ready in 10. I'll pick you up.

382
00:17:23.250 --> 00:17:24.500
Where are we. anyway?

383
00:17:24.500 --> 00:17:25.875
Hope Community Church.

384
00:17:32.625 --> 00:17:34.208
