00:24:30.916 --> 00:24:32.916
You said we should still be friends.

530
00:24:32.916 --> 00:24:36.291
So I thought I'd drop by and wish you luck on the tour.

531
00:24:36.791 --> 00:24:38.416
How friendly of you.

